{
  "stem": "15577.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now when the war was at the end, a few days before the end of the war, the same Czech underground from the surroundings, they knew what he did for us.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They knew how to-- what he was doing during all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they sent a message and told, we know these are the last days of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And if Schindler is left on the Czech soil after the war is finished, he will be sentenced, because he was-- he was a spy against Czechoslovakia before the war.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because we know what he did for-- for you, we give him the chance to disappear now, and to go away from Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was the day-- it was, if I am not mistaken, two days before the end of the war, when he left us-- with 10 of us-- 10 people who worked-- who were-- who were real car mechanics.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we went-- you-- we-- they went with him, 8, 8 of them all-- I don't remember exactly-- went with him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was two cars, with him and his wife.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they went towards West in order to run away from, first of all, from the Czechs, secondly from the Russians.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they arrived until the-- they came to the French/Swiss/German border.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was-- in the meantime, the war ended, so they changed clothes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- ah, we were in-- in Gross Rosen, we got the-- the stripe uniforms.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he got one, and his wife got one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were going, because it was on the way, where the Russians were, the Americans were in the first few days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If they saw a German, they could jail him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he went as a-- as a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
